 Basics First: merge() in R
merge(x, y, by = "common_column")
Works like SQL JOIN
Default is INNER JOIN
Supports all = TRUE (FULL JOIN)
all.x = TRUE (LEFT JOIN)
all.y = TRUE (RIGHT JOIN)
