Product details, sales quantity, and revenue are stored separately and joined using ProductID.
Answer
products <- data.frame(
ProductID = c(1, 2, 3, 4),
ProductName = c("Mobile", "Laptop", "Tablet", "Smart Watch")
)
sales_qty <- data.frame(
ProductID = c(1, 2, 3),
UnitsSold = c(120, 80, 60)
)
